enhanced_by.reason: The iban method relies on the set of supported countries provided by ibanSupportedCountries().
The iban method uses the map created by createCountryCodeToBasicBankAccountNumberPatternMap() to generate IBANs.
The iban method uses the checksum calculated by calculateIbanChecksum() to ensure the IBAN is valid.
The iban method is a wrapper around iban(String) and can be used to verify the correctness of the generated IBAN.
